{"title":"Orto Tratamiento osteoporosis-2026","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Tratamiento osteoporosis-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Tratamiento Osteoporosis","guid":"f2mJeIpUhkaXr5qhTOvZ8Q","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Principios Generales","guid":"rFSjko4PVkysK7h8KDpCzg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Objetivo → prevenir\\Nfracturas por fragilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"**Secuenciación óptima:\\NAnabólico → Antiresortivo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Riesgo inminente → 50% de refracturas en\\Nprimeros 2 años post-fractura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Tiempo para beneficio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Fractura no vertebral → **12.4\\Nmeses** (IC 6.3-18.4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"Fractura de cadera → **20.3\\Nmeses** (IC 11.0-29.7)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"En >80 años → tratamiento razonable si\\Nexpectativa vida >6-12 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Medidas No Farmacológicas","guid":"gLHjN9vzbUu0qwebnef5oQ","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Calcio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Ingesta recomendada → **700-1200\\Nmg/día** (preferir dietético)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Dosis máxima por toma → **500\\Nmg** (saturación absorción)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Carbonato de calcio → tomar con\\Ncomidas (requiere ácido gástrico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"Citrato de calcio →\\Npreferir si uso de IBP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Seguridad CV → metaanálisis\\N2021 muestra ↑ riesgo\\Ncardiovascular con suplementos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"9","text":"Vitamina D","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Deficiencia →\\Ngeneralmente <50\\Nnmol/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Estudios VITAL y D-Health → **NO**\\Nredujeron fracturas en población sana","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Suplementación indicada → deficiencia\\Nsevera, institucionalizados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"9","text":"Calcio + Vitamina D combinados","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Cualquier fractura → **RR\\N0.94** (IC 0.89-0.99)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Fractura cadera → **RR 0.\\N84** (IC 0.72-0.97)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"9","text":"Ejercicio → resistencia\\Nmuscular + balance","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"9","text":"Cesación tabaco y alcohol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Antiresortiva","guid":"V5m7LDhVXEGfDAqngpfgVg","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Bifosfonatos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Primera línea en\\Nmayoría de pacientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Mecanismo → inhiben\\Nosteoclastos, se unen a mineral\\Nóseo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Reducción fracturas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Vertebrales → **50-70%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"No vertebrales → **20-30%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Cadera → **~40%**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"Duración → tras **5 años**, considerar\\Nvacaciones terapéuticas 1-2 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"26","text":"Alendronato","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"70 mg/semana VO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"Contraindicado si eGFR <30-35\\NmL/min (ficha técnica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"26","text":"Zoledrónico (Ácido zoledrónico)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"5 mg IV anual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Puede ser más efectivo que\\Nalendronato → **25% menor riesgo\\Nfractura** (estudio cohorte)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Zoledrónico infrecuente (cada 5\\Naños) → redujo fractura **30%**\\N(IC 23-44%) a 10 años","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"26","text":"Eventos adversos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"**Osteonecrosis mandibular** →\\Nrara, ↑ con uso prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"**Fracturas atípicas de fémur**\\N→ ↑ con uso >5 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Contraindicados VO si\\Npatología digestiva alta","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"25","text":"Denosumab","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Mecanismo →\\Nanticuerpo\\Nanti-RANK-L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"60 mg SC cada 6 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"Eficacia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Similar o superior a\\Nbifosfonatos en DMO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Menor fractura a 2 años vs bifosfonatos\\N→ **RR 0.51** (IC 0.27-0.97)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"**CRÍTICO: Fenómeno de\\Nrebote al suspender**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Fase de resorción rápida\\Npost-suspensión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"Riesgo fracturas vertebrales múltiples →\\N**8-10%** en el año siguiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"**NUNCA suspender sin transición a\\Nbifosfonato** (zoledrónico preferido)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"51","text":"Una dosis de zoledrónico puede no ser\\Nsuficiente → monitorear CTX","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"45","text":"En ERC avanzada (estadio 4-5D) →\\N**hipocalcemia severa y prolongada**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Requiere calcitriol y calcio profiláctico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Manejo por expertos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Anabólica","guid":"pxqfgLKOPk-7uYiDLPMwTQ","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Indicaciones →\\Npacientes muy alto\\Nriesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Fractura vertebral reciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Fractura cadera con T-score ≤-2.5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"Fracturas múltiples","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"59","text":"Teriparatida","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"20 mcg SC diario por hasta 2 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Análogo de PTH →\\Nestimula formación ósea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Eficacia vs risedronato","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Fracturas vertebrales → **HR\\N0.44** (IC 0.29-0.68)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Fracturas clínicas → **HR\\N0.48** (IC 0.32-0.74)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"Seguridad → 15 años vigilancia\\N**NO** aumento osteosarcoma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"64","text":"Limitación previa de 2\\Naños → levantada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"59","text":"Abaloparatida","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Análogo PTHrP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"80 mcg SC diario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Similar eficacia\\Nvertebral a teriparatida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Mejor para fracturas no vertebrales →\\N**OR 0.87** vs teriparatida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Mejor para fracturas cadera →\\N**OR 0.81** vs teriparatida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"59","text":"Romosozumab","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Mecanismo →\\Nanticuerpo\\Nanti-esclerostina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"210 mg SC mensual por 12 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"**Dual: estimula formación\\N+ inhibe resorción**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"Eficacia vs alendronato","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Vertebrales → **RR 0.\\N52** (IC 0.40-0.66)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Clínicas → **RR 0.73** (IC 0.61-0.88)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"Cadera → **RR 0.62** (IC 0.42-0.92)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"78","text":"Aumento DMO → **26%** en HU\\Nespinales en ~10.5 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"**Contraindicado** si\\Nhistoria de IAM o ACV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"78","text":"No repetir segundo año\\Nconsecutivo (pocas ganancias)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"59","text":"Post-anabólico → **SIEMPRE**\\Ntransición a antiresortivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Secuenciación Terapéutica","guid":"aaqNr0DdNUaP19v27wlrLA","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Óptima → Anabólico primero →\\NAntiresortivo después","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Subóptima →\\NAntiresortivo →\\NAnabólico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Bifosfonato previo atenúa ganancia DMO\\Ncon anabólico (~1/3 menos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"Denosumab → Teriparatida → pérdida\\Ntransitoria DMO primeros 12 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"Transición Denosumab → Bifosfonato","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Zoledrónico preferido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Monitorear marcadores\\Nrecambio (CTX)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Puede requerir múltiples dosis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"Situaciones Especiales","guid":"JSvydL0oDUKAc8T1Ts9O-Q","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Enfermedad Renal Crónica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"ERC 3-4 → antiresortivos pueden\\Nreducir fracturas vertebrales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"ERC 5/5D → bifosfonatos\\Ncontraindicados (ficha técnica)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"Evidencia de uso off-label\\Ncon dosis ajustadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"Descartar enfermedad ósea\\Nadinámica primero","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"Denosumab en ERC 4-5D →\\N**alto riesgo hipocalcemia**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"100","text":"Romosozumab → eficaz en\\NeGFR 30-59 mL/min","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"99","text":"Ancianos >80 años","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Tratamiento indicado si\\Nexpectativa vida >6-12 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Eficacia igual o mayor que en jóvenes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Fragilidad → considerar\\N**STOPP-Frail**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"99","text":"Uso de corticoides prolongado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"**START**: bifosfonatos +\\Nvitamina D + calcio obligatorios","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"99","text":"Fractura durante tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"No implica falla → verificar adherencia\\N(>80%) y tiempo (>12 meses)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Descartar causas secundarias (PTH,\\Nmieloma, tiroides, celiaquía)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"Opciones → cambiar a\\Nparenteral o anabólico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"0","text":"Criterios STOPP/START Relevantes","guid":"yI6RFo0CoUCqyLsWLlQXRw","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"**START E3** → Suplementos\\Ncalcio + vitamina D si\\Nosteoporosis conocida o T<-2.5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"**START E4** → Antirresortivos/anabólicos si\\NT<-2.5 o fracturas fragilidad previas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"**STOPP H9** → Bifosfonatos orales\\Ncontraindicados si patología digestiva alta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"Deprescripción bifosfonatos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Tras 5 años tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Si osteonecrosis\\Nmandibular o fractura\\Natípica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"Demencia avanzada o\\Nexpectativa vida limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"Excepción → >75 años, fracturas previas,\\Ncorticoides crónicos, T<-2.5","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"0","text":"Monitorización","guid":"9mRMb2lTN0mfeJlndu_OGQ","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"DMO seriada → valor decreciente,\\Nmayoría mantiene hueso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Marcadores recambio óseo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"CTX → evaluar supresión (mitad\\Ninferior rango premenopáusico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Útil 3-6 meses post-fractura o\\Npost-cambio terapia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"Caídas de DMO grandes en poco\\Ntiempo → sospechar artefacto,\\Ninmovilización o pérdida peso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"Nj28nqD-p0GOOAo2oKnBHw","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"**Secuenciación**: Anabólico\\Nprimero → Antiresortivo después\\Nsiempre que sea posible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"**Denosumab**: NUNCA suspender\\Nsin transición a bifosfonato → riesgo\\Nrebote vertebral múltiple","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"**Calcio**: Máximo 500 mg por toma,\\Npreferir dieta sobre suplementos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"**ERC avanzada + Denosumab**:\\NHipocalcemia severa frecuente →\\Ncalcitriol profiláctico obligatorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"**Fractura en tratamiento**: No es falla\\Nautomática → verificar adherencia >80%\\Ny duración >12 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"132","text":"**Ancianos >80 años**: Tratar si\\Nexpectativa vida >6-12 meses →\\Neficacia demostrada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"132","text":"**Romosozumab**: Contraindicado\\Nsi IAM o ACV previo → señal de\\NMACE en estudio ARCH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"132","text":"**Zoledrónico vs Alendronato**:\\NZoledrónico puede ser superior en\\Neficacia antifractura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"132","text":"**Teriparatida**: Riesgo osteosarcoma\\Ndescartado tras 15 años vigilancia →\\Nrestricción 2 años levantada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"132","text":"**Post-anabólico**: Siempre\\Nconsolidar con antiresortivo →\\Nefecto anabólico es transitorio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"nYyChcqYYUqXjoRpn9uBMg","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"1. Ye C, Ebeling P, Kline G. Osteoporosis.\\NLancet. 2025;406:2003-2016.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"2. Morin SN, Leslie WD, Schousboe\\NJT. Osteoporosis: A Review. JAMA.\\N2025;334(10):894-907.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"3. Reid IR, Billington EO. Drug therapy for\\Nosteoporosis in older adults. Lancet. 2022;\\N399(10329):1080-1092.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"4. Ayers C, et al. Effectiveness and Safety of\\NTreatments to Prevent Fractures. Ann Intern\\NMed. 2023;176(2):182-195.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"5. O'Mahony D, et al.\\NSTOPP/START criteria v2. Age\\NAgeing. 2015;44(2):213-218.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"143","text":"6. Gavilán-Moral E, et al. Ancianos frágiles\\Npolimedicados: deprescripción. Rev Esp Geriatr\\NGerontol. 2012;47(4):162-167.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"143","text":"7. Arriagada L, et al. Polifarmacia y\\Ndeprescripción en personas mayores. Rev\\NMed Clin Condes. 2020;31(2):204-210.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":150,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Tratamiento osteoporosis-2026","id":"map_1544","resolved_references":[]}